    "date": "2021-12-10T15:23:03Z",
    "text": "HOPE for HOMES Act of 2021\n\n This bill provides support for energy efficiency upgrades in homes.\n\n Specifically, the bill directs the Department of Energy (DOE) to establish a grant program that supports training on how to efficiently retrofit homes. In addition, DOE must establish a Home Energy Savings Retrofit Rebate Program to provide rebates for homeowners to invest in energy efficiency improvements."
